quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,Naxariistaha (Allaah)
  55,2,Wuxuu baray Qur'aanka
  55,3,Abuuray aadmiga
  55,4,Baray wada hadalka
  55,5,Qorraxda iyo dayaxu waxay ku socdaan xisaab
  55,6,Oo xiddigaha iyo geedahuba way sujuudaan
  55,7,"Oo samada kor ayuu u qaaday, oo Wuxuu dhigay miisaanka"
  55,8,Si aydaan ugu xadgudbin miisaanka
  55,9,"Oo u hagaajiya miisaanka si caadil ah, oo ha dhimina miisaanka"
  55,10,Oo arlada Waxa uu degaan uga dhigay uunanka nool
  55,11,Dhexdeeda waxaa ah midho iyo geedaha timirta ee fiidaha leh
  55,12,Iyo haruurta leh balka iyo dhir udug wanaagsan leh
  55,13,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,14,Wuxuu ka abuuray Aadmiga dhoobo engegan jilay oo kale ah
  55,15,Oo Wuxuu ka abuuray jinka olol dab
  55,16,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,17,Rabbiga labada bari iyo Rabbiga labada galbeed
  55,18,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,19,Wuxuu ka yeelay labada badood3 inay dareeraan si ay u wada kulmaan
  55,20,"Waxaase dhex yaal shareer, oo iskuma xad gudbaan"
  55,21,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,22,Waxaa ka soo baxa luul mid weyn iyo mid yarba
  55,23,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,24,Oo Isaga baa iska leh doonyaha dhex maaxa4 badda ee buuraha la moodo
  55,25,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,26,Waxa walba oo korkiisa ah waa inay dhintaan
  55,27,Oo waxaa waadhi doonaa abadki Wejiga Rabbigaa Haybadda iyo Sharafta Badan
  55,28,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,29,Kuwaa jira samooyinka iyo arlada baa wax weydiista. Maalin kasta Wuxuu ku sugan yahay xaalad sharaf iyo xurmo leh
  55,30,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,31,"Dhaqso Waanu idiin soo banbixi doonnaa, labadiinna ciidammow"
  55,32,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,33,"Kulanka jinka iyo insigoow! Haddii aad kartaan inaad ka soo gudubtaan nawaaxiga cirarka iyo dhulka, haddaba ka soo gudba. ma ka soo gudbi kartaan amar la'aan"
  55,34,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,35,"Olol naar ah, qiiq, iyo maar (la dhalaaliyey)6 baa la idinku soo deyn, mana kari doontaan inaad is difaacdaan"
  55,36,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,37,"Ee marka ay samadu kala dillaacdo, oo markaas ay noqoto gaduud sida idiinta"
  55,38,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin8 beenineysaan
  55,39,Maalintaas Insi iyo Jinba waxba lagama weydiin doono dambigooda
  55,40,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,41,"Dambiilayaasha waxaa lagu aqoonsan astaamahooda, markaas baa laga soo qaban foodaha iyo cagaha"
  55,42,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,43,Tanu waa Naartii ay dambiilayaashu beeniyeen
  55,44,Waxay ku meereyesan dhexdooda iyada iyo biyaha kulul ee karaya
  55,45,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,46,"Oo kan isaga ka cabsada hor istaagga Rabbigi, waxaa uu mudan labo beerood"
  55,47,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,48,Oo leh noocyo kala duwan oo badan
  55,49,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,50,Dhexdooda waxaa ah labo ilood oo dur dur ah
  55,51,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,52,Waxaaa ku yaal midho walba oo mid kastaa lammaane tahay
  55,53,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,54,"Iyagoo ku jiqlaynaya firaashyo cudbi-goodu xariir yahay, oo midhaha labadaa beerood waxay ahaan kuwo goosi dhow"
  55,55,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,56,Waxaa jooga kuwaa soo laaba araggooda ka hor iyaga aanu taaban insi iyo jin midkoodna
  55,57,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,58,La moodo dheeman iyo luul
  55,59,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,60,Miyey tahay abaalgudka samaanta wax kale aan ahayn samaan
  55,61,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,62,"Oo barbarkooda labadatani, waxaa ah labo beerood oo kale"
  55,63,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,64,Labaduba u janjeera madow cagaaran
  55,65,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,66,Dhexdooda waxaa ah labo ilood oo burqanaya
  55,67,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,68,"Waxaa dhexdooda ah midho, geedo timir iyo Rummaan"
  55,69,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,70,Waxaa dhexdooda ah khayraat iyo qurux badnooyin
  55,71,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,72,Xuurulceyn ku kooban oo aan ka bixin khaymadahooda
  55,73,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,74,Oo ka hore iyaga aanu taaban insi iyo jin midkoodna
  55,75,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,76,Iyagoo ku jiqleynaya barkimooyin cagaaran iyo gogollo qurux badan
  55,77,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,78,"Waxaa khayr iyo barako badan Magaca Rabbigaa, Weynaha, Sharafta Badan"